        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Not to mention another big point, the surrounding spawns are really quite easy to solo with the the 49 pet and the undead slow. If you do bring enough people to take the Sprie Lord, your group will fall asleep hunting the rest of the area. Given his long spawn time, lack of interesting drops, lack of anything else to around the area, this entire area is kind of a waste. I cannot really think of a compelling reason anyone would want to hunt him, past the fact that his graphic kicks ass. </P><P>Now if only Verant had provided that graphic for a necromancers Lich form (which it should look like anyways) I know a lot of necros would have the "O face". Too bad they wasted this graphic on an area that few people will ever bother hunting. </P><P>Cheers,<BR>Ancagalon the Black</P><P></P><P>Edited by - ancagalon on 01/22/2002  12:04:26<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
