        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I havent been able to solo him completely, but I did it at 51 with a 47 necro.  You should be able to do it by yourself with a higher pet.  </P><P>Pull pet and park on the wall by the grey.  Buff up and Med to at least half.  Run over to the peak in front of the spire, target the lord (you wont be able to see him but you can target him by clicking about where he is on the tower).  Run over to where you can cast.  Cast some non disease based DoT, run back to the peak and wait.  When he comes for you run him to the grey zone and circle the area in front of it.  When pet gains agro, nuke, DoT, or whatever you can get on him, til he starts chasing again.  Ten, 15 mins, you can kill him.  </P><P></P><P>Smaaug Darqsmoke<BR>Iksar Necromancer<BR>Brell Serilis<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
